      "source": [
        "#Cambio de info de la columna de experiencia para tener solo 3 tipos(senior, semisenior, junior)\n",
        "\n",
        "def experience(row):\n",
        "  if row.experience_level == 'SE':\n",
        "    return 'Senior'\n",
        "  elif row.experience_level == 'MI':\n",
        "    return 'Semi Senior'\n",
        "  else:\n",
        "    return 'Junior'\n",
        "\n",
        "df.experience_level = df.apply(experience, axis='columns') \n"
